 The centre of Bae U and Kemz Mama also known as Mummy Wa’s enviable relationship can no longer hold and it’s already getting shrouded in melodrama. Per the account of Gistlovers who seems to have exclusive scoop on celebs in Nigeria and to some extent Ghana all the time, the relationship has crashed owing to Bae U’s constant cheating and domestic violence. Kemz, meanwhile has reportedly secured the services of a lawyer to legally fight her former heartthrob, claiming the house Bae U is living in right now equally belongs to her as she contributed money towards its acquisition. The post read; ”Hello tueh tueh, Mummy Wa and Isbae You separates due to domestic vawulence and Bae You p** no dey stay one place, be like na for telegram this gist go sweet, so we can share pictures freely without restrictions. The post read; ”Hello tueh tueh, Mummy Wa and Isbae You separates due to domestic vawulence and Bae You p** no dey stay one place, be like na for telegram this gist go sweet, so we can share pictures freely without restrictions. Mother of side chic involved, then Mummy Wa is involving her lawyer too because according to information house wey Bae U buy, him and Mummy Wa gather money buy am ni, mummy think say the matter go end for marriage. As it is now everywhere don turn yam pepper scatter scatter them dey beat mummy wa join the money wey she dey donate for the relationship.”